UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat5.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(_DigiDistore);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat3.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat3.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat2.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _DigiST1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DigiPow;

};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;

in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;

{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);

    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_16 = u_xlat16_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_2.z = max(u_xlat16_30, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.xz = min(u_xlat16_2.xz, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);

    for(uint u_xlatu_loop_1 = uint(0u) ; u_xlatu_loop_1<u_xlatu0 ; u_xlatu_loop_1++)
    {
        u_xlat28 = float(int(u_xlatu_loop_1));
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb15 = !!(u_xlat28<2.0);

        u_xlatb15 = u_xlat28<2.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_10.xy = (bool(u_xlatb15)) ? unity_LightIndices[0].xy : unity_LightIndices[0].zw;
        u_xlat29 = u_xlat28 + -2.0;
        u_xlat28 = (u_xlatb15) ? u_xlat28 : u_xlat29;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb28 = !!(u_xlat28<1.0);
#else
        u_xlatb28 = u_xlat28<1.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_30 = (u_xlatb28) ? u_xlat16_10.x : u_xlat16_10.y;
        u_xlati28 = int(u_xlat16_30);
        u_xlat15.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz) + _AdditionalLightsPosition[u_xlati28].xyz;
        u_xlat5.x = dot(u_xlat15.xyz, u_xlat15.xyz);
        u_xlat5.x = max(u_xlat5.x, 6.10351563e-05);
        u_xlat19 = inversesqrt(u_xlat5.x);
        u_xlat15.xyz = u_xlat15.xyz * vec3(u_xlat19);
        u_xlat19 = float(1.0) / float(u_xlat5.x);
        u_xlat5.x = u_xlat5.x * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati28].x + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati28].y;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat5.x = min(max(u_xlat5.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat5.x = clamp(u_xlat5.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat5.x = u_xlat5.x * u_xlat19;
        u_xlat16_30 = dot(_AdditionalLightsSpotDir[u_xlati28].xyz, u_xlat15.xyz);
        u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_30 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati28].z + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati28].w;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_30 = min(max(u_xlat16_30, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_30 = clamp(u_xlat16_30, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_30 * u_xlat16_30;
        u_xlat5.x = u_xlat16_30 * u_xlat5.x;
        u_xlat16_30 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat15.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_30 = min(max(u_xlat16_30, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_30 = clamp(u_xlat16_30, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_30) * _AdditionalLightsColor[u_xlati28].xyz;
        u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat5.xxx * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
        u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    }
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat11.xyz, u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_2.xy = u_xlat16_2.xx * u_xlat11.xy;
    u_xlat16_2.xy = u_xlat16_2.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_2.xy = u_xlat16_2.xy * _RampMap_ST.xy + _RampMap_ST.zw;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_RampMap, u_xlat16_2.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.www * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat0.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz / u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb42 = !!(_DigiBaseColor1.w<0.00999999978);
#else
    u_xlatb42 = _DigiBaseColor1.w<0.00999999978;
#endif
    u_xlat16_2.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (u_xlatb42) ? -1.0 : u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat42 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat1.xy = vec2(u_xlat42) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat1.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat16_42 = texture(_ClothTex, u_xlat1.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_16 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_16 = min(u_xlat16_16, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_16 * u_xlat16_2.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat42 = u_xlat16_42 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat42 = (-u_xlat16_2.x) + u_xlat42;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat42 = min(max(u_xlat42, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat42 = clamp(u_xlat42, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.x = log2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat1.x = exp2(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat1.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat15.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = (-_DigiBaseColor0.xyz) * u_xlat1.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat42) * u_xlat0.xyz + u_xlat15.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;

    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;

    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);

void main()
{
    u_xlat10_0 = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat10_1 = texture2D(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(abs(u_xlat10_1.z));
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_16 = u_xlat10_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat10_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_2.z = max(u_xlat16_30, 0.0399999991);

    u_xlat1.x = log2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat1.x = exp2(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat1.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat15.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = (-_DigiBaseColor0.xyz) * u_xlat1.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat42) * u_xlat0.xyz + u_xlat15.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}

UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(_DigiDistore);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _RampMap;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
uint u_xlatu0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
bool u_xlatb5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
vec3 u_xlat7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
float u_xlat12;
uint u_xlatu12;
vec3 u_xlat13;
mediump float u_xlat16_14;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_16;
float u_xlat17;
vec3 u_xlat20;
float u_xlat24;
int u_xlati24;
bool u_xlatb24;
mediump float u_xlat16_26;
float u_xlat32;
float u_xlat36;
mediump float u_xlat16_36;
bool u_xlatb36;
mediump float u_xlat16_38;
mediump float u_xlat16_39;
float u_xlat41;
mediump float u_xlat16_42;
float u_xlat43;
mediump float u_xlat16_46;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_1.z));
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat16_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_26 = u_xlat16_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_2.z = max(u_xlat16_26, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.xz = min(u_xlat16_2.xz, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat16_1.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat16_38 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_39 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_39 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat13.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_39 = (-u_xlat16_14) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_39 = (-u_xlat16_39) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat16_14;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_14 = min(max(u_xlat16_14, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_14 = clamp(u_xlat16_14, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif

uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
uniform 	mediump float _FurTilling;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

void main()
{
    u_xlat10_0 = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat10_1 = texture2D(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(abs(u_xlat10_1.z));
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat10_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_26 = u_xlat10_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_2.z = max(u_xlat16_26, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.xz = min(u_xlat16_2.xz, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat10_1.xyz = texture2D(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat10_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat10_1.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat16_38 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_39 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_39 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat13.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_39 = (-u_xlat16_14) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_39 = (-u_xlat16_39) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat16_14;
    u_xlat16_14 = clamp(u_xlat16_14, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = (-u_xlat10_0.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_14) + u_xlat10_0.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_14) * u_xlat7.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_14 = (-u_xlat16_2.z) + u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat16_14 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_14 = clamp(u_xlat16_14, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_2.z * u_xlat16_2.z;
    u_xlat41 = u_xlat16_39 * u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat13.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = abs(u_xlat16_4.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(u_xlat16_4.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat43 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat43 = clamp(u_xlat43, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat8.x = dot(u_xlat13.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat8.x = clamp(u_xlat8.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat20.x = u_xlat16_3.y * u_xlat16_3.y;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat16_3.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat20.z = u_xlat20.x * 0.125 + u_xlat32;
    u_xlat20.x = u_xlat20.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat32);
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat20.zx + vec2(0.125, 0.125);
    u_xlat16_16.xy = max(u_xlat9.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_16.xy = u_xlat16_16.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_16.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_16.xyz = u_xlat16_16.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_16.xyz = u_xlat16_16.xyz * _SHColorScale.xyz;
    u_xlat16_42 = dot((-u_xlat13.xyz), u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_42 + u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * (-vec3(u_xlat16_42)) + (-u_xlat13.xyz);
    u_xlat20.x = (-u_xlat16_4.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat20.x * u_xlat20.x;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_42 * u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat16_16.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_16.xyz;
    u_xlat16_46 = (-u_xlat16_2.z) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_46 = u_xlat16_2.z * u_xlat16_46;
    u_xlat16_46 = u_xlat16_46 * 6.0;
    u_xlat10_9 = textureCube(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_10.xyz, u_xlat16_46);
    u_xlat16_10.x = u_xlat10_9.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_10.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_10.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_10.x = max(u_xlat16_10.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_10.x = log2(u_xlat16_10.x);
    u_xlat16_10.x = u_xlat16_10.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_10.x = exp2(u_xlat16_10.x);
    u_xlat16_10.x = u_xlat16_10.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat10_9.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xxx;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat20.x = u_xlat16_39 * u_xlat16_39 + 1.0;
    u_xlat20.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat20.x;
    u_xlat20.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * u_xlat20.xxx;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-u_xlat7.xyz) + vec3(u_xlat16_14);
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_42) * u_xlat9.xyz + u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat20.xyz = u_xlat20.xyz * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat20.xyz = u_xlat16_16.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat20.xyz;
    u_xlat16_16.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat5.x = (-u_xlat43) * u_xlat43 + 1.0;
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat16_39 * u_xlat43;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat17 * u_xlat17 + u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat16_39 / u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat5.x * u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat16_2.z * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat5.x * u_xlat17;
    u_xlat5.x = min(u_xlat5.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);

    u_xlat1.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat3.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat3.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat2.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

#endif

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(7) uniform mediump sampler2D _RampMap;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
uint u_xlatu0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
bool u_xlatb5;
vec4 u_xlat6;
bool u_xlatb6;
vec3 u_xlat7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
float u_xlat13;
uint u_xlatu13;
vec3 u_xlat14;
mediump float u_xlat16_15;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_17;
float u_xlat18;
vec3 u_xlat20;
float u_xlat26;
int u_xlati26;
bool u_xlatb26;
mediump float u_xlat16_28;
mediump float u_xlat16_30;
float u_xlat33;
float u_xlat39;
mediump float u_xlat16_39;
bool u_xlatb39;
mediump float u_xlat16_41;
mediump float u_xlat16_42;
mediump float u_xlat16_43;
float u_xlat44;
bool u_xlatb44;
float u_xlat45;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_1.z));
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_15 = u_xlat16_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_2.z = max(u_xlat16_28, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.xz = min(u_xlat16_2.xz, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_1.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_41 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_42 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_42 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_42);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_42) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat6.xy,u_xlat6.z);
    u_xlat6.x = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    vec3 txVec1 = vec3(u_xlat7.xy,u_xlat7.z);
    u_xlat6.y = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec1, 0.0);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    vec3 txVec2 = vec3(u_xlat7.xy,u_xlat7.z);
    u_xlat6.z = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec2, 0.0);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    vec3 txVec3 = vec3(u_xlat7.xy,u_xlat7.z);
    u_xlat6.w = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec3, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_42 = dot(u_xlat6, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_43 = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_42 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_43;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb44 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb44 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb6 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb6 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb44 = u_xlatb44 || u_xlatb6;
    u_xlat16_42 = (u_xlatb44) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat16_43 = (-u_xlat16_15) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_43 = (-u_xlat16_43) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_15 = u_xlat16_15;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15 = min(max(u_xlat16_15, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15 = clamp(u_xlat16_15, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-u_xlat16_0.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_15) + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_15) * u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_15 = (-u_xlat16_2.z) + u_xlat16_43;
    u_xlat16_15 = u_xlat16_15 + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15 = min(max(u_xlat16_15, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15 = clamp(u_xlat16_15, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_43 = u_xlat16_2.z * u_xlat16_2.z;
    u_xlat44 = u_xlat16_43 * u_xlat16_43;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat7.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.x = min(max(u_xlat1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat14.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = abs(u_xlat16_4.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(u_xlat16_4.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat45 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat45 = min(max(u_xlat45, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat45 = clamp(u_xlat45, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat7.x = dot(u_xlat14.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat7.x = min(max(u_xlat7.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat7.x = clamp(u_xlat7.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat20.x = u_xlat16_3.y * u_xlat16_3.y;
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat16_3.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat20.z = u_xlat20.x * 0.125 + u_xlat33;
    u_xlat20.x = u_xlat20.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat33);
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat20.zx + vec2(0.125, 0.125);
    u_xlat16_17.xy = max(u_xlat9.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_17.xy = u_xlat16_17.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_17.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * _SHColorScale.xyz;
    u_xlat16_17.x = dot((-u_xlat14.xyz), u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_17.x + u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * (-u_xlat16_17.xxx) + (-u_xlat14.xyz);
    u_xlat20.x = (-u_xlat16_4.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat20.x * u_xlat20.x;
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_17.x * u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_30 = (-u_xlat16_2.z) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_2.z * u_xlat16_30;
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_30 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_9 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_11.xyz, u_xlat16_30);
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_9.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_30 = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_30 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_30 = max(u_xlat16_30, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_30 = log2(u_xlat16_30);
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_30 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_30 = exp2(u_xlat16_30);
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_30 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_30);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat20.x = u_xlat16_43 * u_xlat16_43 + 1.0;
    u_xlat20.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat20.x;
    u_xlat20.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat20.xxx;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-u_xlat6.xyz) + vec3(u_xlat16_15);
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xxx * u_xlat9.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat20.xyz = u_xlat20.xyz * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat20.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat20.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_42) * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat5.x = (-u_xlat45) * u_xlat45 + 1.0;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat16_43 * u_xlat45;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat18 * u_xlat18 + u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat16_43 / u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat5.x * u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat16_2.z * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat5.x * u_xlat18;
    u_xlat5.x = min(u_xlat5.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = min(u_xlat16_10.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);

    u_xlat16_11.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_12.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = max(u_xlat16_11.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = min(u_xlat16_11.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyw = vec3(u_xlat16_41) * u_xlat10_0.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_42 = min(_AdditionalLightsCount.x, unity_LightData.y);
    u_xlati0 = int(u_xlat16_42);
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat45 * u_xlat44 + (-u_xlat45);
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat13 * u_xlat45 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat13 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat13 * u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat44 / u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat16_28 = (-u_xlat16_2.z) * u_xlat16_2.z + 1.0;
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_28 + u_xlat16_43;
    u_xlat26 = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat16_28 + u_xlat16_43;
    u_xlat26 = u_xlat26 * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat13 + u_xlat26;
    u_xlat13 = 0.5 / u_xlat16_28;
    u_xlat26 = (-u_xlat7.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat26 * u_xlat26;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat5.x * u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat26 * u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat6.y * 50.0;
    u_xlat16_28 = clamp(u_xlat16_28, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_17.x = (-u_xlat26) * u_xlat5.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * u_xlat16_17.xxx;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_28) * vec3(u_xlat18) + u_xlat16_17.xyz;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat13 * u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_28) * u_xlat16_17.xyz + vec3(-6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05);
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = max(u_xlat16_17.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = min(u_xlat16_17.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * vec3(0.318309873, 0.318309873, 0.318309873) + u_xlat16_17.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyw;
    for(int u_xlati_loop_1 = 0 ; u_xlati_loop_1<u_xlati0 ; u_xlati_loop_1++)
    {
        u_xlat26 = float(u_xlati_loop_1);
        u_xlatb5 = u_xlat26<2.0;
        u_xlat16_10.xy = (bool(u_xlatb5)) ? unity_LightIndices[0].xy : unity_LightIndices[0].zw;
        u_xlat18 = u_xlat26 + -2.0;
        u_xlat26 = (u_xlatb5) ? u_xlat26 : u_xlat18;
        u_xlatb26 = u_xlat26<1.0;
        u_xlat16_28 = (u_xlatb26) ? u_xlat16_10.x : u_xlat16_10.y;
        u_xlati26 = int(u_xlat16_28);
        u_xlat5.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz) + _AdditionalLightsPositionDynamicIndex(u_xlati26).xyz;
        u_xlat44 = dot(u_xlat5.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
        u_xlat44 = max(u_xlat44, 6.10351563e-05);
        u_xlat6.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat44);
        u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * u_xlat6.xxx;
        u_xlat6.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat44;
        u_xlat44 = u_xlat44 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati26).x + _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati26).y;
        u_xlat44 = clamp(u_xlat44, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat44 = u_xlat44 * u_xlat6.x;
        u_xlat16_28 = dot(_AdditionalLightsSpotDirDynamicIndex(u_xlati26).xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
        u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_28 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati26).z + _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati26).w;
        u_xlat16_28 = clamp(u_xlat16_28, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_28 * u_xlat16_28;
        u_xlat44 = u_xlat16_28 * u_xlat44;
        u_xlat16_28 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
        u_xlat16_28 = clamp(u_xlat16_28, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_28) * _AdditionalLightsColorDynamicIndex(u_xlati26).xyz;
        u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat44) * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
        u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    }
    u_xlat0.xyz = (-u_xlat14.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat14.zxy) + (-u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat5.x = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat5.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat5.x);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat5.xxx;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat0.yzx * (-u_xlat14.zxy);
    u_xlat5.xyz = (-u_xlat14.yzx) * u_xlat0.zxy + (-u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat44 = dot(u_xlat5.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat44 = inversesqrt(u_xlat44);
    u_xlat5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat44) * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(u_xlat5.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot((-u_xlat14.xyz), u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_2.xy = u_xlat0.xy * u_xlat16_2.xx;
    u_xlat16_2.xy = u_xlat16_2.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_2.xy = u_xlat16_2.xy * _RampMap_ST.xy + _RampMap_ST.zw;
    u_xlat10_0.xyz = texture2D(_RampMap, u_xlat16_2.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat10_0.www * u_xlat10_0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat0.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz / u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlatb39 = _DigiBaseColor1.w<0.00999999978;
    u_xlat16_2.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (u_xlatb39) ? -1.0 : u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat39 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat1.xy = vec2(u_xlat39) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat1.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat10_39 = texture2D(_ClothTex, u_xlat1.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_15 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_15 = min(u_xlat16_15, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_15 * u_xlat16_2.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat39 = u_xlat10_39 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat39 = (-u_xlat16_2.x) + u_xlat39;
    u_xlat39 = clamp(u_xlat39, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat1.x = log2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat1.x = exp2(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat1.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = (-_DigiBaseColor0.xyz) * u_xlat1.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat39) * u_xlat0.xyz + u_xlat14.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(_DigiDistore);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MetallicOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _NormalScale;

	UNITY_UNIFORM float _DigiDistore;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _RampMap_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHColorScale;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MatMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _RampMap;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
vec3 u_xlat13;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
float u_xlat14;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_18;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_19;
mediump float u_xlat16_22;
mediump float u_xlat16_24;
float u_xlat26;
mediump float u_xlat16_30;
mediump float u_xlat16_36;
float u_xlat37;
mediump float u_xlat16_37;
bool u_xlatb37;
float u_xlat38;
float u_xlat39;
mediump float u_xlat16_42;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_0.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_0.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat13.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-u_xlat13.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat13.zxy) + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = (-u_xlat13.zxy) * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat4.xyz = (-u_xlat13.yzx) * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_0.xy = u_xlat16_0.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyw = u_xlat16_0.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_0.xyw;
    u_xlat16_36 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_36 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_36);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_36) * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat4.y = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat4.x = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat4.z = dot((-u_xlat13.xyz), u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_36 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat13.xyz);
    u_xlat16_36 = abs(u_xlat16_36) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_36 = min(u_xlat16_36, 1.0);
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_6.x = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_6.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_6.x);
    u_xlat16_6.xy = u_xlat4.xy * u_xlat16_6.xx;
    u_xlat16_6.xy = u_xlat16_6.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_6.xy = u_xlat16_6.xy * _RampMap_ST.xy + _RampMap_ST.zw;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = texture(_RampMap, u_xlat16_6.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat3.xy = u_xlat1.xx * u_xlat4.xy;
    u_xlat3.xy = u_xlat3.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_4 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_4.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_6.x = max(u_xlat16_6.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_6.x = min(u_xlat16_6.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_18.x = (-u_xlat16_6.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_18.x * u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_18.x * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = textureLod(_MatMap, u_xlat3.xy, u_xlat16_18.x).xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * vec3(_MatMapMul);
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_6.x * u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_7.x * u_xlat16_7.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat16_36) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_18.x * u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_4.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_42 = (-u_xlat16_30) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_30;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_30 = min(max(u_xlat16_30, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_30 = clamp(u_xlat16_30, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_42 = (-u_xlat16_42) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_42 = (-u_xlat16_6.x) + u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_42 + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_42 = min(max(u_xlat16_42, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_42 = clamp(u_xlat16_42, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_5 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_30) * u_xlat8.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_19.xyz = (-u_xlat16_5.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_30) + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_42) + (-u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xxx * u_xlat9.xyz + u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_0.y * u_xlat16_0.y;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat16_0.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat39 = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + u_xlat38;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat38);
    u_xlat4.y = u_xlat1.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat4.x = u_xlat39 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_18.xy = max(u_xlat4.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_18.xy = u_xlat16_18.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_18.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xyz * _SHColorScale.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_4.z));
    u_xlat16_22 = u_xlat16_4.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_22 = u_xlat16_22 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_10.x = u_xlat16_10.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_10.x = exp2(u_xlat16_10.x);
    u_xlat16_10.x = min(u_xlat16_10.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xxx;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xyz * u_xlat16_19.xyz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.x = _SHshadow + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_18.x = min(max(u_xlat16_18.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_18.x = clamp(u_xlat16_18.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.x = min(max(u_xlat1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat2.x = (-u_xlat1.x) * u_xlat1.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_7.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_7.x / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_6.x * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat14 = u_xlat16_6.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat14 = u_xlat14 * u_xlat14;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat1.x = min(u_xlat1.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat2.xzw = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.x = min(max(u_xlat1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat2.xzw = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat2.xzw;
    u_xlat2.xzw = u_xlat2.xzw * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xzw = u_xlat2.xzw * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat4.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = u_xlat4.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = min(u_xlat16_6.xzw, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat2.xzw * u_xlat16_6.xzw;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_19.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xzw + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * u_xlat16_18.xxx + u_xlat16_6.xzw;
    u_xlat16_42 = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_42 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_42);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_42) * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_42 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_7.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_42 = min(max(u_xlat16_42, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_42 = clamp(u_xlat16_42, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_42) * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = max(u_xlat16_7.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = min(u_xlat16_7.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_42 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_42 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_42);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_42) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.x = dot(u_xlat16_7.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_0.x = min(max(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_0.x = clamp(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_10.x * u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_12.x = (-u_xlat16_36) + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = log2(u_xlat16_36);
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat2.x = exp2(u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat2.x = (-u_xlat2.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat26 = u_xlat14 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_24 = (-u_xlat14) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_24 + u_xlat26;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_12.x / u_xlat16_24;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_0.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_12.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_12.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_12.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_0.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_0.x = min(max(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_0.x = clamp(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_0.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * u_xlat16_12.x;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_5.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * u_xlat16_0.xxx;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = max(u_xlat16_0.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = min(u_xlat16_0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_22) * u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * u_xlat16_5.www;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = (-_DigiBaseColor0.xyz) * u_xlat2.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb37 = !!(_DigiBaseColor1.w<0.00999999978);
#else
    u_xlatb37 = _DigiBaseColor1.w<0.00999999978;
#endif
    u_xlat16_0.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_0.x = (u_xlatb37) ? -1.0 : u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_0.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat16_12.x = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_12.x = min(u_xlat16_12.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_0.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat37 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat3.xy = vec2(u_xlat37) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat3.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat3.xy;
    u_xlat16_37 = texture(_ClothTex, u_xlat3.xy).x;
    u_xlat37 = u_xlat16_37 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat37 = (-u_xlat16_0.x) + u_xlat37;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat37 = min(max(u_xlat37, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat37 = clamp(u_xlat37, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat37) * u_xlat1.xyz + u_xlat2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif

attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;

vec3 u_xlat3;

float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

    u_xlat16_0.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_0.x = (u_xlatb37) ? -1.0 : u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_0.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat16_12.x = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_12.x = min(u_xlat16_12.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_0.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat37 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat3.xy = vec2(u_xlat37) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat3.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat3.xy;
    u_xlat10_37 = texture2D(_ClothTex, u_xlat3.xy).x;
    u_xlat37 = u_xlat10_37 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat37 = (-u_xlat16_0.x) + u_xlat37;
    u_xlat37 = clamp(u_xlat37, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat37) * u_xlat1.xyz + u_xlat2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}

UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat5.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(_DigiDistore);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat3.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat3.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat2.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _MatMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(7) uniform mediump sampler2D _RampMap;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec4 u_xlat0;
bool u_xlatb0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
vec3 u_xlat10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
vec3 u_xlat12;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
bool u_xlatb12;
float u_xlat13;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_14;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_19;
float u_xlat25;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_26;
mediump float u_xlat16_31;
float u_xlat36;
mediump float u_xlat16_36;
bool u_xlatb36;
float u_xlat37;
mediump float u_xlat16_38;
mediump float u_xlat16_39;
float u_xlat40;
mediump float u_xlat16_43;
mediump float u_xlat16_45;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat0.xy,u_xlat0.z);
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    vec3 txVec1 = vec3(u_xlat1.xy,u_xlat1.z);
    u_xlat0.y = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec1, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    vec3 txVec2 = vec3(u_xlat1.xy,u_xlat1.z);
    u_xlat0.z = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec2, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    vec3 txVec3 = vec3(u_xlat1.xy,u_xlat1.z);
    u_xlat0.w = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec3, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat0, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_14.x = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_14.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb0 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb12 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb12 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlatb12 || u_xlatb0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (u_xlatb0) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat16_2.x + _SHshadow;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_14.x = min(max(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_14.x = clamp(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_3.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_3.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_3.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = (-u_xlat12.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat12.zxy) + (-u_xlat4.xyz);

    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;

    u_xlat5.xyz = (-u_xlat12.yzx) * u_xlat4.zxy + (-u_xlat5.xyz);

    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);

    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_26.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;

    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;

    u_xlat16_26.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_26.x);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_26.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat5.y = dot(u_xlat5.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat5.x = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat5.z = dot((-u_xlat12.xyz), u_xlat16_3.xyz);

    u_xlat16_26.x = abs(u_xlat16_26.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat5.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat16_38 = dot(u_xlat5.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat16_38 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_38);

#endif

#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];

uniform 	mediump float _FurTilling;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

#define SV_Target0 gl_FragData[0]

void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat0.xy).x;
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlat0.x<u_xlat0.z;
    u_xlat0.x = (u_xlatb0) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat1.xy).x;
    u_xlatb1 = u_xlat1.x<u_xlat1.z;
    u_xlat0.y = (u_xlatb1) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat1.xy).x;
    u_xlatb1 = u_xlat1.x<u_xlat1.z;
    u_xlat0.z = (u_xlatb1) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;

    u_xlat16_2.x = (u_xlatb0) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_2.x;

    u_xlat16_14.x = clamp(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0, 1.0);

    u_xlat16_3.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;

    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);

    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat5.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;

    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat10_6.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);

    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_26.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;

    u_xlat16_26.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_26.x);

    u_xlat5.z = dot((-u_xlat12.xyz), u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_26.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat12.xyz);
    u_xlat16_26.x = abs(u_xlat16_26.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat5.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat16_38 = dot(u_xlat5.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat16_38 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_38);
    u_xlat16_7.xy = vec2(u_xlat16_38) * u_xlat5.xy;
    u_xlat16_7.xy = u_xlat16_7.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_7.xy = u_xlat16_7.xy * _RampMap_ST.xy + _RampMap_ST.zw;
    u_xlat10_12.xyz = texture2D(_RampMap, u_xlat16_7.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat4.xy = u_xlat0.xx * u_xlat5.xy;
    u_xlat4.xy = u_xlat4.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat10_5 = texture2D(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat10_5.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_26.y = max(u_xlat16_38, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_26.xy = min(u_xlat16_26.xy, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat16_39 = (-u_xlat16_26.y) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_26.y * u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_39 * 6.0;

    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_26.y * u_xlat16_26.y;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_39 * u_xlat16_39 + 1.0;
    u_xlat0.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx;
    u_xlat0.x = (-u_xlat16_26.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_7.x * u_xlat16_7.x;
    u_xlat16_19.x = u_xlat10_5.x + _MetallicOffset;

    u_xlat16_19.x = u_xlat16_19.x;
    u_xlat16_19.x = clamp(u_xlat16_19.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_31 = (-u_xlat16_31) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_31 = (-u_xlat16_26.y) + u_xlat16_31;
    u_xlat16_31 = u_xlat16_31 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_31 = clamp(u_xlat16_31, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat10_6 = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);

    u_xlat10.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xxx * u_xlat10.xyz + u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz * u_xlat10.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_3.y * u_xlat16_3.y;

    u_xlat40 = u_xlat0.x * 0.125 + u_xlat37;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat37);

    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat40 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_7.xy = max(u_xlat5.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));

    u_xlat16_19.xyz = u_xlat16_7.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_19.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * _SHColorScale.xyz;
    u_xlat16_43 = log2(abs(u_xlat10_5.z));
    u_xlat16_45 = u_xlat10_5.w * _EmisssionScale;

    u_xlat16_43 = u_xlat16_43 * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_43 = exp2(u_xlat16_43);
    u_xlat16_43 = min(u_xlat16_43, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_43) * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat0.x) * u_xlat0.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_39 * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_39 / u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;

    u_xlat13 = u_xlat16_26.y + 1.0;
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat13 * u_xlat13;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat0.x = min(u_xlat0.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat1.xzw;
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat1.xzw * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat1.xzw * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat5.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = min(u_xlat16_7.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat1.xzw * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz * u_xlat16_14.xxx + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_14.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_14.x);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_9.xyz);
    u_xlat16_14.x = clamp(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xxx * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = max(u_xlat16_9.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = min(u_xlat16_9.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_14.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_14.x);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.x = dot(u_xlat16_9.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_14.x = clamp(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat16_43 * u_xlat16_14.x;
    u_xlat16_38 = (-u_xlat16_26.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = log2(u_xlat16_26.x);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat1.x = exp2(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat1.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat25 = u_xlat13 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_26.x = (-u_xlat13) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_26.x = u_xlat16_38 * u_xlat16_26.x + u_xlat25;
    u_xlat16_26.x = u_xlat16_38 / u_xlat16_26.x;
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat16_26.x * u_xlat16_14.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_26.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_26.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_26.x;
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat16_26.x * u_xlat16_14.x;
    u_xlat16_14.x = clamp(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_26.x = u_xlat16_14.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat16_14.x * u_xlat16_14.x;
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat16_14.x * u_xlat16_26.x;
    u_xlat16_26.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_26.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_14.x;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat10_6.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat10_6.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_3.xyz + u_xlat16_14.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = max(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = min(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_45) * u_xlat10_6.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat10_12.xyz * u_xlat10_6.www;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = (-_DigiBaseColor0.xyz) * u_xlat1.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlatb36 = _DigiBaseColor1.w<0.00999999978;
    u_xlat16_2.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (u_xlatb36) ? -1.0 : u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat16_14.x = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_14.x = min(u_xlat16_14.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_14.x * u_xlat16_2.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat36 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat4.xy = vec2(u_xlat36) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat4.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat4.xy;
    u_xlat10_36 = texture2D(_ClothTex, u_xlat4.xy).x;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat10_36 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat36 = (-u_xlat16_2.x) + u_xlat36;
    u_xlat36 = clamp(u_xlat36, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat36) * u_xlat0.xyz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LightmapST;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAr;

#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
