#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
uniform 	mediump vec4 unity_WorldTransformParams;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
uniform 	mediump float _FurTilling;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _FurTilling;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Metallic;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Smoothness;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Cutoff;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _BumpScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _EmissionColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SketchHalftoneMin;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SketchHalftoneMax;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SketchColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RampThreshold;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RampSmooth;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AOScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ActorScaleAttribute;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _FurShape;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Rimlightoffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _viweoffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHshadow;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _RimLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MatMapMul;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SunShiftOffuse1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SunShiftOffuse2;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SunShift;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _specularColor1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _glossiness_1X;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _glossiness_1Y;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _specularColor2;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _glossiness_2X;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _glossiness_2Y;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DigiChange;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _DigiBaseColor0;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _DigiBaseColor1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _DigiHighColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _DigiST1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DigiPow;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _DigiDistore;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _RampMap_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHColorScale;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(_DigiDistore);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _RampMap;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;
vec4 u_xlat5;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_6;
vec3 u_xlat7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
vec3 u_xlat10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
float u_xlat12;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
float u_xlat17;
mediump float u_xlat16_18;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_25;
mediump float u_xlat16_30;
float u_xlat36;
mediump float u_xlat16_36;
bool u_xlatb36;
mediump float u_xlat16_37;
float u_xlat38;
mediump float u_xlat16_39;
float u_xlat41;
float u_xlat43;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_0.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_1.x = max(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_1.x = min(u_xlat16_1.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_13.x = (-u_xlat16_1.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_25.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_25.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_25.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_25.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_25.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_25.x);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_25.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat12 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat12 = max(u_xlat12, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat12 = inversesqrt(u_xlat12);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat12) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(u_xlat12) + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_25.x = dot((-u_xlat2.xyz), u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_25.x = u_xlat16_25.x + u_xlat16_25.x;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * (-u_xlat16_25.xxx) + (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_13.x);
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_4.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_13.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_13.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_13.x = max(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_13.x = log2(u_xlat16_13.x);
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_13.x = exp2(u_xlat16_13.x);
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_13.xxx;
    u_xlat16_39 = log2(abs(u_xlat16_0.z));
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_39 * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_39 = exp2(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_39 = min(u_xlat16_39, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat16_6.x * u_xlat16_6.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat12 = float(1.0) / u_xlat12;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * vec3(u_xlat12);
    u_xlat16_13.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_13.x = abs(u_xlat16_13.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_13.x = min(u_xlat16_13.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat12 = (-u_xlat16_13.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_25.x = u_xlat12 * u_xlat12;
    u_xlat16_25.x = u_xlat16_25.x * u_xlat16_25.x;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_0.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_18 = u_xlat16_0.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_18 = u_xlat16_18 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_30 = (-u_xlat16_37) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_37;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_37 = min(max(u_xlat16_37, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_37 = clamp(u_xlat16_37, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_30 = (-u_xlat16_30) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_30 = (-u_xlat16_1.x) + u_xlat16_30;
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_30 + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_30 = min(max(u_xlat16_30, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_30 = clamp(u_xlat16_30, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_37) * u_xlat8.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = (-u_xlat16_0.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_37) + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_30) + (-u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat10.xyz = u_xlat16_25.xxx * u_xlat10.xyz + u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat7.xyz * u_xlat10.xyz;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat16_3.y * u_xlat16_3.y;
    u_xlat41 = u_xlat16_3.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat43 = u_xlat38 * 0.125 + u_xlat41;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat41);
    u_xlat10.y = u_xlat38 + 0.125;
    u_xlat10.x = u_xlat43 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_25.xy = max(u_xlat10.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_25.xy = u_xlat16_25.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_25.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_25.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * _SHColorScale.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_25.x = _SHshadow + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_25.x = min(max(u_xlat16_25.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_25.x = clamp(u_xlat16_25.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat38 = dot(u_xlat5.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat38 = inversesqrt(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat38) * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat38 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat38 = min(max(u_xlat38, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat38 = clamp(u_xlat38, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat5.x = (-u_xlat38) * u_xlat38 + 1.0;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat16_6.x * u_xlat38;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat38 + u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat16_6.x / u_xlat38;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat38;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat16_1.x * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat16_1.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat17 * u_xlat17;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat38 = min(u_xlat38, 100.0);
    u_xlat5.xzw = vec3(u_xlat38) * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat38 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat38 = min(max(u_xlat38, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat38 = clamp(u_xlat38, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat5.xzw = vec3(u_xlat38) * u_xlat5.xzw;
    u_xlat5.xzw = u_xlat5.xzw * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xzw = u_xlat5.xzw * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat8.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = u_xlat8.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = min(u_xlat16_6.xzw, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat5.xzw * u_xlat16_6.xzw;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat38) * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = u_xlat16_9.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xzw + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xzw = u_xlat7.xyz * u_xlat16_25.xxx + u_xlat16_6.xzw;
    u_xlat16_6.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_6.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_6.x);
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = u_xlat16_6.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xzw);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_6.x = min(max(u_xlat16_6.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_6.x = clamp(u_xlat16_6.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = u_xlat16_6.xxx * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = u_xlat16_1.xzw * u_xlat16_6.xzw;
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = max(u_xlat16_6.xzw, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = min(u_xlat16_6.xzw, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xzw = u_xlat16_1.xzw + u_xlat16_6.xzw;
    u_xlat16_6.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_6.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_6.x);
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = u_xlat16_6.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.x = dot(u_xlat16_6.xzw, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_6.x = min(max(u_xlat16_6.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_6.x = clamp(u_xlat16_6.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_39 * u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat17 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_6.x = (-u_xlat17) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_30 = (-u_xlat16_13.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat17 = log2(u_xlat16_13.x);
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat17 * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat17 = exp2(u_xlat17);
    u_xlat17 = (-u_xlat17) + 2.0;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_30 * u_xlat16_6.x + u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_30 / u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_39 + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_39 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_39 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_39;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_13.x = min(max(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_13.x = clamp(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_13.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = u_xlat16_0.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_0.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xzw;
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = u_xlat16_13.xxx * u_xlat16_6.xzw;
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = max(u_xlat16_6.xzw, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = min(u_xlat16_6.xzw, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xzw + u_xlat16_6.xzw;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_18) * u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = (-u_xlat2.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat2.zxy) + (-u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat5.x = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat5.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat5.x);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat5.xxx;
    u_xlat5.xzw = u_xlat0.yzx * (-u_xlat2.zxy);
    u_xlat5.xzw = (-u_xlat2.yzx) * u_xlat0.zxy + (-u_xlat5.xzw);
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot((-u_xlat2.xyz), u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat2.x = dot(u_xlat5.xzw, u_xlat5.xzw);
    u_xlat2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xxx * u_xlat5.xzw;
    u_xlat0.y = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_37 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_37 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_37);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat0.xy * vec2(u_xlat16_37);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * _RampMap_ST.xy + _RampMap_ST.zw;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_RampMap, u_xlat16_3.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_0.www * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat38) + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * u_xlat0.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz / u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat0.xyz = (-_DigiBaseColor0.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat17) + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat17) * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb36 = !!(_DigiBaseColor1.w<0.00999999978);
#else
    u_xlatb36 = _DigiBaseColor1.w<0.00999999978;
#endif
    u_xlat16_1.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (u_xlatb36) ? -1.0 : u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat16_13.x = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_13.x = min(u_xlat16_13.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_1.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat36 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat5.xy = vec2(u_xlat36) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat5.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat5.xy;
    u_xlat16_36 = texture(_ClothTex, u_xlat5.xy).x;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat16_36 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat36 = (-u_xlat16_1.x) + u_xlat36;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat36 = min(max(u_xlat36, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat36 = clamp(u_xlat36, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat36) * u_xlat0.xyz + u_xlat2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;

vec4 u_xlat0;

void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;

    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;

    gl_Position = u_xlat1;

    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;

    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);

    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

#endif

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _RampMap;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;
vec4 u_xlat5;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_6;
vec3 u_xlat7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
vec3 u_xlat10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
float u_xlat12;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
float u_xlat17;
mediump float u_xlat16_18;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_25;
mediump float u_xlat16_30;
float u_xlat36;
mediump float u_xlat16_36;
bool u_xlatb36;
mediump float u_xlat16_37;
float u_xlat38;
mediump float u_xlat16_39;
float u_xlat41;
float u_xlat43;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_0.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_1.x = max(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_1.x = min(u_xlat16_1.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_13.x = (-u_xlat16_1.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_25.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_25.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_25.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_25.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_25.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_25.x);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_25.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat12 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat12 = max(u_xlat12, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat12 = inversesqrt(u_xlat12);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat12) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(u_xlat12) + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_25.x = dot((-u_xlat2.xyz), u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_25.x = u_xlat16_25.x + u_xlat16_25.x;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * (-u_xlat16_25.xxx) + (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_13.x);
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_4.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_13.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_13.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_13.x = max(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_13.x = log2(u_xlat16_13.x);
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_13.x = exp2(u_xlat16_13.x);
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_13.xxx;
    u_xlat16_39 = log2(abs(u_xlat16_0.z));
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_39 * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_39 = exp2(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_39 = min(u_xlat16_39, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat16_6.x * u_xlat16_6.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat12 = float(1.0) / u_xlat12;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * vec3(u_xlat12);
    u_xlat16_13.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_13.x = abs(u_xlat16_13.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_13.x = min(u_xlat16_13.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat12 = (-u_xlat16_13.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_25.x = u_xlat12 * u_xlat12;
    u_xlat16_25.x = u_xlat16_25.x * u_xlat16_25.x;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_0.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_18 = u_xlat16_0.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_18 = u_xlat16_18 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_30 = (-u_xlat16_37) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_37;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_37 = min(max(u_xlat16_37, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_37 = clamp(u_xlat16_37, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_30 = (-u_xlat16_30) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_30 = (-u_xlat16_1.x) + u_xlat16_30;
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_30 + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_30 = min(max(u_xlat16_30, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_30 = clamp(u_xlat16_30, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_37) * u_xlat8.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = (-u_xlat16_0.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_37) + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_30) + (-u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat10.xyz = u_xlat16_25.xxx * u_xlat10.xyz + u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat7.xyz * u_xlat10.xyz;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat16_3.y * u_xlat16_3.y;
    u_xlat41 = u_xlat16_3.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat43 = u_xlat38 * 0.125 + u_xlat41;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat41);
    u_xlat10.y = u_xlat38 + 0.125;
    u_xlat10.x = u_xlat43 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_25.xy = max(u_xlat10.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_25.xy = u_xlat16_25.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_25.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_25.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * _SHColorScale.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_25.x = _SHshadow + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_25.x = min(max(u_xlat16_25.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_25.x = clamp(u_xlat16_25.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat38 = dot(u_xlat5.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat38 = inversesqrt(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat38) * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat38 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat38 = min(max(u_xlat38, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat38 = clamp(u_xlat38, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat5.x = (-u_xlat38) * u_xlat38 + 1.0;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat16_6.x * u_xlat38;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat38 + u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat16_6.x / u_xlat38;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat38;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat16_1.x * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat16_1.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat17 * u_xlat17;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat38 = min(u_xlat38, 100.0);
    u_xlat5.xzw = vec3(u_xlat38) * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat38 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat38 = min(max(u_xlat38, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat38 = clamp(u_xlat38, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat5.xzw = vec3(u_xlat38) * u_xlat5.xzw;
    u_xlat5.xzw = u_xlat5.xzw * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xzw = u_xlat5.xzw * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat8.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = u_xlat8.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = min(u_xlat16_6.xzw, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat5.xzw * u_xlat16_6.xzw;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat38) * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = u_xlat16_9.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xzw + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xzw = u_xlat7.xyz * u_xlat16_25.xxx + u_xlat16_6.xzw;
    u_xlat16_6.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_6.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_6.x);
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = u_xlat16_6.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xzw);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_6.x = min(max(u_xlat16_6.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_6.x = clamp(u_xlat16_6.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = u_xlat16_6.xxx * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = u_xlat16_1.xzw * u_xlat16_6.xzw;
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = max(u_xlat16_6.xzw, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = min(u_xlat16_6.xzw, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xzw = u_xlat16_1.xzw + u_xlat16_6.xzw;
    u_xlat16_6.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_6.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_6.x);
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = u_xlat16_6.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.x = dot(u_xlat16_6.xzw, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_6.x = min(max(u_xlat16_6.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_6.x = clamp(u_xlat16_6.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_39 * u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat17 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_6.x = (-u_xlat17) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_30 = (-u_xlat16_13.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat17 = log2(u_xlat16_13.x);
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat17 * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat17 = exp2(u_xlat17);
    u_xlat17 = (-u_xlat17) + 2.0;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_30 * u_xlat16_6.x + u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_30 / u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_39 + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_39 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_39 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_39;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_13.x = min(max(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_13.x = clamp(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_13.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = u_xlat16_0.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_0.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xzw;
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = u_xlat16_13.xxx * u_xlat16_6.xzw;
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = max(u_xlat16_6.xzw, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = min(u_xlat16_6.xzw, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xzw + u_xlat16_6.xzw;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_18) * u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = (-u_xlat2.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat2.zxy) + (-u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat5.x = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat5.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat5.x);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat5.xxx;
    u_xlat5.xzw = u_xlat0.yzx * (-u_xlat2.zxy);
    u_xlat5.xzw = (-u_xlat2.yzx) * u_xlat0.zxy + (-u_xlat5.xzw);
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot((-u_xlat2.xyz), u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat2.x = dot(u_xlat5.xzw, u_xlat5.xzw);
    u_xlat2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xxx * u_xlat5.xzw;
    u_xlat0.y = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_37 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_37 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_37);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat0.xy * vec2(u_xlat16_37);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * _RampMap_ST.xy + _RampMap_ST.zw;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_RampMap, u_xlat16_3.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_0.www * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat38) + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * u_xlat0.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz / u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat0.xyz = (-_DigiBaseColor0.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat17) + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat17) * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb36 = !!(_DigiBaseColor1.w<0.00999999978);
#else
    u_xlatb36 = _DigiBaseColor1.w<0.00999999978;
#endif
    u_xlat16_1.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (u_xlatb36) ? -1.0 : u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat16_13.x = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_13.x = min(u_xlat16_13.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_1.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat36 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat5.xy = vec2(u_xlat36) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat5.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat5.xy;
    u_xlat16_36 = texture(_ClothTex, u_xlat5.xy).x;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat16_36 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat36 = (-u_xlat16_1.x) + u_xlat36;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat36 = min(max(u_xlat36, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat36 = clamp(u_xlat36, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat36) * u_xlat0.xyz + u_xlat2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

{

    u_xlat16_6.x = clamp(u_xlat16_6.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = u_xlat16_6.xxx * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = u_xlat16_1.xzw * u_xlat16_6.xzw;
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = max(u_xlat16_6.xzw, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = min(u_xlat16_6.xzw, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xzw = u_xlat16_1.xzw + u_xlat16_6.xzw;
    u_xlat16_6.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_6.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_6.x);
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = u_xlat16_6.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.x = dot(u_xlat16_6.xzw, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_6.x = clamp(u_xlat16_6.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_39 * u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat17 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_6.x = (-u_xlat17) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_30 = (-u_xlat16_13.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat17 = log2(u_xlat16_13.x);
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat17 * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat17 = exp2(u_xlat17);
    u_xlat17 = (-u_xlat17) + 2.0;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_30 * u_xlat16_6.x + u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_30 / u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_39 + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_39 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_39 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_13.x = clamp(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_13.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = u_xlat10_0.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat10_0.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xzw;
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = u_xlat16_13.xxx * u_xlat16_6.xzw;
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = max(u_xlat16_6.xzw, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = min(u_xlat16_6.xzw, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xzw + u_xlat16_6.xzw;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_18) * u_xlat10_0.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = (-u_xlat2.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat2.zxy) + (-u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat5.x = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat5.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat5.x);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat5.xxx;
    u_xlat5.xzw = u_xlat0.yzx * (-u_xlat2.zxy);
    u_xlat5.xzw = (-u_xlat2.yzx) * u_xlat0.zxy + (-u_xlat5.xzw);
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot((-u_xlat2.xyz), u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat2.x = dot(u_xlat5.xzw, u_xlat5.xzw);
    u_xlat2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xxx * u_xlat5.xzw;
    u_xlat0.y = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_37 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_37 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_37);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat0.xy * vec2(u_xlat16_37);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * _RampMap_ST.xy + _RampMap_ST.zw;
    u_xlat10_0.xyz = texture2D(_RampMap, u_xlat16_3.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat10_0.www * u_xlat10_0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat38) + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * u_xlat0.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz / u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat0.xyz = (-_DigiBaseColor0.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat17) + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat17) * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlatb36 = _DigiBaseColor1.w<0.00999999978;
    u_xlat16_1.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (u_xlatb36) ? -1.0 : u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat16_13.x = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_13.x = min(u_xlat16_13.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_1.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat36 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat5.xy = vec2(u_xlat36) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat5.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat5.xy;
    u_xlat10_36 = texture2D(_ClothTex, u_xlat5.xy).x;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat10_36 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat36 = (-u_xlat16_1.x) + u_xlat36;
    u_xlat36 = clamp(u_xlat36, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat36) * u_xlat0.xyz + u_xlat2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif
"

 Pass {
  Name "OUTLINE"
  LOD 300
  Tags { "IGNOREPROJECTOR" = "true" "LIGHTMODE" = "AdvancedOutline" "QUEUE" = "Geometry+200" "RenderType" = "Transparent" }
  Cull Front
  GpuProgramID 69515
Program "vp" {
SubProgram "gles " {
Keywords { "_VCOLOR2N_OFF" "_VTEX_OFF" }
"// hash: 7372a2dfa20d9f7c
#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec4 _ScreenParams;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
uniform 	mediump vec4 _OutlineColor;
uniform 	mediump float _Offset;
uniform 	vec4 _lightDir;
uniform 	vec4 _ScreenResolution;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_COLOR0;
varying mediump float vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
float u_xlat6;
float u_xlat9;
float u_xlat10;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = 0.0;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = max(u_xlat9, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat9 = dot(_lightDir.xyz, _lightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * _lightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-_OutlineColor.xyz) + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat3.xyz + _OutlineColor.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * in_COLOR0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1.w = 1.0;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_NORMAL0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_NORMAL0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_NORMAL0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xz = u_xlat0.yy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].xy * u_xlat0.xx + u_xlat3.xz;
    u_xlat0.xy = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].xy * u_xlat0.zz + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat6 = dot(u_xlat0.xy, u_xlat0.xy);
    u_xlat6 = inversesqrt(u_xlat6);
    u_xlat0.xy = vec2(u_xlat6) * u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy / _ScreenParams.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy * _ScreenResolution.yy;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat6 = u_xlat1.y * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].w;
    u_xlat6 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].w * u_xlat1.x + u_xlat6;
    u_xlat6 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].w * u_xlat1.z + u_xlat6;
    u_xlat6 = u_xlat6 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].w;
    u_xlat0.xy = vec2(u_xlat6) * u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy * vec2(0.00462962966, 0.00462962966);
    u_xlat2.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[0].x;
    u_xlat2.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[1].y;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy / u_xlat2.xy;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat1.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[0].xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[2].xyz * u_xlat1.zzz + u_xlat1.xyw;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat0.xy + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat0.xy, u_xlat0.xy);
    u_xlat0.x = sqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 0.00100000005);
    u_xlat3.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat3.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat3.x);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xxx * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz / abs(u_xlat3.zzz);
    u_xlat10 = abs(_Offset) * 0.150000006;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat10;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 100.0;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[0].z;
    u_xlat1.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[1].z;
    u_xlat1.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[2].z;
    u_xlat1.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[3].z;
    u_xlat0.w = 1.0;
    gl_Position.z = dot(u_xlat1, u_xlat0);
    u_xlat1.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[0].x;
    u_xlat1.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[2].x;
    u_xlat1.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[3].x;
    gl_Position.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat1.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[1].y;
    u_xlat1.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[2].y;
    u_xlat1.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[3].y;
    gl_Position.y = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat0.yzw);
    u_xlat0.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[2].w;
    u_xlat0.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[3].w;
    gl_Position.w = dot(u_xlat0.xy, u_xlat0.zw);
    return;
}

    u_xlat1.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[3].y;
    gl_Position.y = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat0.yzw);
    u_xlat0.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[2].w;
    u_xlat0.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[3].w;
    gl_Position.w = dot(u_xlat0.xy, u_xlat0.zw);
    return;
}

    precision highp float;
#else
    precision mediump float;
#endif

varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;

void main()
{
    SV_Target0.xyz = max(vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;

#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(binding = x, std140)
#else
#define UNITY_LOCATION(x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(std140)
#endif

#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _OutlineMap;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump float vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
float u_xlat9;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = 0.0;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = max(u_xlat9, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat9 = dot(_lightDir.xyz, _lightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * _lightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat0.x = min(max(u_xlat0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-_OutlineColor.xyz) + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat3.xyz + _OutlineColor.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = textureLod(_OutlineMap, in_TEXCOORD0.xy, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat1.w * abs(_Offset);
    vs_TEXCOORD1.w = 1.0;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_NORMAL0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_NORMAL0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_NORMAL0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat3.yy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].xy;
    u_xlat3.xy = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].xy * u_xlat3.xx + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat3.xy = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].xy * u_xlat3.zz + u_xlat3.xy;
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat3.xy, u_xlat3.xy);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat3.xy = vec2(u_xlat9) * u_xlat3.xy;
    u_xlat3.xy = u_xlat3.xy / _ScreenParams.xy;
    u_xlat3.xy = u_xlat3.xy * _ScreenResolution.yy;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat1.y * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].w;
    u_xlat9 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].w * u_xlat1.x + u_xlat9;
    u_xlat9 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].w * u_xlat1.z + u_xlat9;
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat9 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].w;
    u_xlat0.yz = vec2(u_xlat9) * u_xlat3.xy;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.150000006, 0.00462962966, 0.00462962966);
    u_xlat2.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[0].x;
    u_xlat2.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[1].y;
    u_xlat3.xy = u_xlat0.yz / u_xlat2.xy;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat1.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[0].xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[2].xyz * u_xlat1.zzz + u_xlat1.xyw;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat3.xy + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat3.x = dot(u_xlat3.xy, u_xlat3.xy);
    u_xlat3.x = sqrt(u_xlat3.x);
    u_xlat3.x = max(u_xlat3.x, 0.00100000005);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat3.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 100.0;
    u_xlat3.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat3.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat3.x);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xxx * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz / abs(u_xlat3.zzz);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[0].z;
    u_xlat1.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[1].z;
    u_xlat1.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[2].z;
    u_xlat1.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[3].z;
    u_xlat0.w = 1.0;
    gl_Position.z = dot(u_xlat1, u_xlat0);
    u_xlat1.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[0].x;
    u_xlat1.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[2].x;
    u_xlat1.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[3].x;
    gl_Position.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat1.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[1].y;
    u_xlat1.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[2].y;
    u_xlat1.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[3].y;
    gl_Position.y = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat0.yzw);
    u_xlat0.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[2].w;
    u_xlat0.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[3].w;
    gl_Position.w = dot(u_xlat0.xy, u_xlat0.zw);

{
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = 0.0;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);

    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat9 = dot(_lightDir.xyz, _lightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * _lightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat0.x = min(max(u_xlat0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-_OutlineColor.xyz) + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);

    u_xlat1 = textureLod(_OutlineMap, in_TEXCOORD0.xy, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat1.xyz;

    u_xlat0.xyz = in_NORMAL0.yzx * in_TANGENT0.zxy + (-u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * in_TANGENT0.www;

    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;

    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy * _ScreenResolution.yy;

    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;

    u_xlat2.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[1].y;

    u_xlat1.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[0].xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[2].xyz * u_xlat1.zzz + u_xlat1.xyw;

    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);

    u_xlat1.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[0].z;
    u_xlat1.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[1].z;
    u_xlat1.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[2].z;

    u_xlat1.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[2].x;

    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat12 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat12 = max(u_xlat12, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat12 = inversesqrt(u_xlat12);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat12) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_1 = min(u_xlat16_1, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_1 = (-u_xlat16_1) + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(0.0500000007, 0.0500000007, 0.0500000007);

varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD2;
#define SV_Target0 gl_FragData[0]
float u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
lowp vec2 u_xlat10_3;
bool u_xlatb9;
mediump float u_xlat16_10;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0 = vs_TEXCOORD1.w * vs_TEXCOORD2.w;
    u_xlat16_1.x = _DigiChange;
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2 = (-_DigiBaseColor0) + _DigiBaseColor1;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_1.xxxx * u_xlat16_2 + _DigiBaseColor0;
    u_xlat10_3.xy = texture2D(_ClothTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xy;
    u_xlatb9 = u_xlat16_1.w>=u_xlat10_3.x;
    u_xlat16_10 = (u_xlatb9) ? u_xlat0 : 0.0;
    u_xlat16_10 = u_xlat10_3.x * u_xlat16_10;
    u_xlat16_2.x = _DigiChange + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (-u_xlat16_2.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat10_3.y * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * vs_TEXCOORD2.z;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * _DigiHighColor.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_10) * u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}
SubProgram "gles3 " {

"// hash: 8ceded18fe865ebf
#ifdef VERTEX
#version 300 es

#define HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS 1
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
#define UNITY_UNIFORM
#else
#define UNITY_UNIFORM uniform
#endif
#define UNITY_SUPPORTS_UNIFORM_LOCATION 1
#if UNITY_SUPPORTS_UNIFORM_LOCATION
#define UNITY_LOCATION(x) layout(location = x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(binding = x, std140)
#else
#define UNITY_LOCATION(x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(std140)
#endif
uniform 	vec4 _Time;
uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(1) uniform UnityPerDraw {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LODFade;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_WorldTransformParams;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_LightData;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_LightIndices[2];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_ProbesOcclusion;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SpecCube0_HDR;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_DynamicLightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAr;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAg;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAb;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBr;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBg;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBb;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHC;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(0) uniform UnityPerMaterial {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _OutlineColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _OutlineWidth;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Offset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _lightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _ScreenResolution;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _DigiST1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DigiChange;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _DigiBaseColor0;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _DigiBaseColor1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _DigiHighColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _DigiScale;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_COLOR0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD2;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
float u_xlat4;
bool u_xlatb4;
float u_xlat8;
float u_xlat12;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).y;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.z = 0.0;
    u_xlat4 = u_xlat0.x * in_TEXCOORD0.y + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.xy = min(u_xlat16_1.xx, vec2(1.0, 0.0));
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb4 = !!(u_xlat4>=u_xlat16_1.y);
#else
    u_xlatb4 = u_xlat4>=u_xlat16_1.y;
#endif
    u_xlat4 = u_xlatb4 ? 1.0 : float(0.0);
    u_xlat8 = (-u_xlat4) * u_xlat0.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat4;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_1.y * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (-u_xlat16_1.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat0.xyw = u_xlat0.xxx * in_NORMAL0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.w = u_xlat8;
    u_xlat2.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(0.0500000007, 0.0500000007, 0.0500000007);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * vec3(_DigiScale) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyw * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat3.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat3.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat12 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat12 = max(u_xlat12, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat12 = inversesqrt(u_xlat12);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat12) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.w = min(max(u_xlat1.w, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.w = clamp(u_xlat1.w, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_COLOR0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat12 = in_TEXCOORD0.y * 2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat1.z = (-_DigiChange) * 2.0 + u_xlat12;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.z = min(max(u_xlat1.z, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.z = clamp(u_xlat1.z, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.xyw = in_TEXCOORD0.xyy;
    vs_TEXCOORD2 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

#endif

    u_xlat16_2 = (-_DigiBaseColor0) + _DigiBaseColor1;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_1.xxxx * u_xlat16_2 + _DigiBaseColor0;
    u_xlat16_3.xy = texture(_ClothTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xy;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb9 = !!(u_xlat16_1.w>=u_xlat16_3.x);
#else
    u_xlatb9 = u_xlat16_1.w>=u_xlat16_3.x;

uniform 	vec4 _DigiST1;
uniform 	mediump float _DigiChange;
uniform 	float _DigiScale;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_COLOR0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD2;
vec4 u_xlat0;
mediump float u_xlat16_1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
float u_xlat12;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = vec2(0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat12 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);

    u_xlat16_1 = min(u_xlat16_1, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_1 = (-u_xlat16_1) + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(0.0500000007, 0.0500000007, 0.0500000007);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_1) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * vec3(_DigiScale) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat2.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat2.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat2.zzz + u_xlat2.xyw;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-u_xlat2.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat0.w = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat0.w = clamp(u_xlat0.w, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_COLOR0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0.x = in_TEXCOORD0.y * 2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat0.z = (-_DigiChange) * 2.0 + u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.z = clamp(u_xlat0.z, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat0.xyw = in_TEXCOORD0.xyy;
    vs_TEXCOORD2 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat2.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat2.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat2.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;

    u_xlat4 = u_xlat0.x * in_TEXCOORD0.y + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.xy = min(u_xlat16_1.xx, vec2(1.0, 0.0));
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb4 = !!(u_xlat4>=u_xlat16_1.y);
#else
    u_xlatb4 = u_xlat4>=u_xlat16_1.y;
#endif
    u_xlat4 = u_xlatb4 ? 1.0 : float(0.0);
    u_xlat8 = (-u_xlat4) * u_xlat0.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat4;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_1.y * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (-u_xlat16_1.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat0.xyw = u_xlat0.xxx * in_NORMAL0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.w = u_xlat8;
    u_xlat2.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(0.0500000007, 0.0500000007, 0.0500000007);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * vec3(_DigiScale) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyw * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat3.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat3.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat12 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat12 = max(u_xlat12, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat12 = inversesqrt(u_xlat12);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat12) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.w = min(max(u_xlat1.w, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.w = clamp(u_xlat1.w, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_COLOR0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat12 = in_TEXCOORD0.y * 2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat1.z = (-_DigiChange) * 2.0 + u_xlat12;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.z = min(max(u_xlat1.z, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.z = clamp(u_xlat1.z, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.xyw = in_TEXCOORD0.xyy;
    vs_TEXCOORD2 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

#endif
#ifdef FRAGMENT
#version 300 es

precision highp float;
precision highp int;
#define HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS 1
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
#define UNITY_UNIFORM
#else
#define UNITY_UNIFORM uniform
#endif
#define UNITY_SUPPORTS_UNIFORM_LOCATION 1
#if UNITY_SUPPORTS_UNIFORM_LOCATION
#define UNITY_LOCATION(x) layout(location = x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(binding = x, std140)
#else
#define UNITY_LOCATION(x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(std140)
#endif
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(0) uniform UnityPerMaterial {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _OutlineColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _OutlineWidth;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Offset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _lightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _ScreenResolution;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _DigiST1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DigiChange;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _DigiBaseColor0;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _DigiBaseColor1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _DigiHighColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _DigiScale;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD2;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
float u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_3;
bool u_xlatb9;
mediump float u_xlat16_10;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0 = vs_TEXCOORD1.w * vs_TEXCOORD2.w;
    u_xlat16_1.x = _DigiChange;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_1.x = min(max(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2 = (-_DigiBaseColor0) + _DigiBaseColor1;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_1.xxxx * u_xlat16_2 + _DigiBaseColor0;
    u_xlat16_3.xy = texture(_ClothTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xy;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb9 = !!(u_xlat16_1.w>=u_xlat16_3.x);
#else
    u_xlatb9 = u_xlat16_1.w>=u_xlat16_3.x;
#endif
    u_xlat16_10 = (u_xlatb9) ? u_xlat0 : 0.0;
    u_xlat16_10 = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_10;
    u_xlat16_2.x = _DigiChange + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (-u_xlat16_2.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_3.y * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * vs_TEXCOORD2.z;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * _DigiHighColor.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_10) * u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}

{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _BaseMap_ST.xy + _BaseMap_ST.zw;

    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;

    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);

    u_xlat6 = dot(_LightDirection.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat6 = clamp(u_xlat6, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat6 = (-u_xlat6) + 1.0;
    u_xlat6 = u_xlat6 * _ShadowBias.y;

    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    gl_Position.z = max((-u_xlat0.w), u_xlat0.z);
    gl_Position.xyw = u_xlat0.xyw;
    return;
